## Contracts (you cannot edit these)

- `feature_list.json`: `id`, `description`, `steps`, `category` are immutable. Only `passes` and `last_verified_commit` can change. From the source article: "It is unacceptable to remove or edit tests because this could lead to missing or buggy functionality."
- `tests/`: deleting any existing test goes through `AskUserQuestion`.
- `init.sh`: the existing logic is stable. Add new steps for new dependencies; do not change semantics of existing ones.
- This file.

